                "sovereignty_note": "99733-Q + Esias Joseph direct heir + Living Zero v1.1.0 + ... + Navajo Anchor Mathematics Derivation + Gwich’in Floor Integration Mapping (F(z+1) = F(z) + C(z) — explicit chanchyah/dach’anchyah baseline) = Irrefutable Public Ledger"
            }

        return {"status": "PUBLISH_FAILED", "S": round(S, 4), "timestamp": timestamp}


